{"tid":1633452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武！和理非！哨兵！全世界同我入down咗佢！！！","createTime":"2019-10-07T04:06:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T09:44:19.000Z","uid":105530,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ee938069c879643801d68a0fa7597958fcb1a3be","tid":1633452,"uid":105530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:06:13.000Z","msg":"見到之前唔少巴打絲打都提出要用顏色指示後排情況 方便前進或撤退<br />\n<br />\n鑒於呢個情況 就喺呢度推薦一個Apps俾大家用！<br />\n就係<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">ShowWhat</span></span><br />\n<br />\n佢係可以調校<br />\n-個mon出現咩顏色<br />\n-顏色閃動嘅頻率<br />\n-手機電筒閃動嘅頻率<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">更加重要嘅係</span><br />\n<br />\n開啟<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">藍牙</span>就可以將調校嘅設定運用係所有人手機度！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9cq84uD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9cq84uD.png&h=c527beaf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nn828Wm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnn828Wm.png&h=dfaa59bf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UztFVBn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUztFVBn.png&h=939e05b4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/unonpuJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FunonpuJ.png&h=1ebe2460&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cMTq6H4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcMTq6H4.png&h=23cf0546&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n勇武喺前面未必有手用電話<br />\n咁就靠中前排嘅人聽到前線指示即刻用呢個app將顏色散播開去<br />\n唔使重蹈覆轍 好似10.6咁 退又退唔到走又走唔到<br />\n<br />\n之前已經有手足講過<br />\n但現場實用使用率唔夠<br />\n越多嘅人down佢嘅功效先越大<br />\n希望有用<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">光復香港</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和勇不分！</span></span>"},{"pid":"7a599fc2d5b9512698962e8f24ff736cf30c26ac","tid":1633452,"uid":105530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:07:02.000Z","msg":"和勇不分！"},{"pid":"4c6bd1c55d88e2e3c096904fdc9bb3c283ca0fe6","tid":1633452,"uid":105530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:07:14.000Z","msg":"和勇不分！！"},{"pid":"7bd679a412c56d40ee6e0f8899901e26e4c2e18e","tid":1633452,"uid":105530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:07:37.000Z","msg":"和勇不分！！！"},{"pid":"f4ca9e1f6f6baf0e5f37074e0752da7e10a5a6b0","tid":1633452,"uid":80303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:07:38.000Z","msg":"依啲就有用竹post la"},{"pid":"b4f1cfec920a00d4ed83abb77d18c282798422a8","tid":1633452,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:07:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f003ace01aaad40680e9030d4a9e4a67b12fdcdb","tid":1633452,"uid":105530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:08:03.000Z","msg":"和勇不分！！！！"},{"pid":"9a5cb1b759ef949a7c5a8a10005f3d2e8230c192","tid":1633452,"uid":105530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:08:41.000Z","msg":"快啲down咗佢好有用架！！！！"},{"pid":"00f989058ee85068d60d06538dbde1262ec690fa","tid":1633452,"uid":72065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:09:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f079b0b7504579ba5ccec090da81fb589d902d6","tid":1633452,"uid":105530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:09:42.000Z","msg":"哨兵！！入！！"},{"pid":"19f7527ca2855e3853e11bbb2a24ebacc16ba8ad","tid":1633452,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:09:59.000Z","msg":"冷氣軍師都做到既野<br />\n<br />\n全民哨兵，好過大聲嗌"},{"pid":"d928a524a7e8cc5347f1f67e1b9e193e22d